attributes.name: Vape Cartridge-Ekto Cooler .5g
attributes.body:
Strain: Hybrid

Fragrance: Orange, lemon, lemongrass

Effects: Uplifting, euphoric

Ekto Kooler is a blast from the past, sent to the future to haunt your taste
buds. Layers of citrus ooze from this flavor, while light pineapple and
fruit notes add depth. Itll scare you into a good mood.
